description: Do you have what it takes to master Dynamical? JDF Software brings you the next great puzzle game. Test your wits and your patience, trying to match the game board to the solution. Each move takes you closer to the goal, but beware - for every action there's a reaction - and that's what Dynamical is all about. A tutorial walks you through the rules of the game, then it is up to you to master. The levels start off easy, then get progressively more difficult. Can you beat all the levels and achieve the global high score? Real beta tester review: "JDF has hit a HOME FRICKIN RUN!! ... Once you figure out how to pass the levels, the game is very addicting! ... Very challenging and fun." - This lite version has 7 levels. If that's not enough, get the full version of Dynamical with many more levels & updates. (HINT: There IS a cheat code built in to Dynamical - can you figure out what it is???)
